         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">28/3/95 ¶  ¶ Would you be so kind, esteemed Professor, as to refer to this note? ¶  It cannot be about the  ¶ Atriplex ¶  species of Australia, certainly highly important for California, because the w...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">95.03.28</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Eugene Hilgard</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Bancroft Library, University of California, Berkeley, California.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">28/3/95</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Wollen Sie so freundlich sein, geehrter Herr Professor, worauf sich diese Notiz bezieht. Es kann nicht sein auf die für Californien gewiss hochwichtigen <name key="Atriplex">Atriplex</name> Arten Australiens, da der Schreiber seine Pflanze mit <name key="Medicago%20sativa">Medicago sativa</name> vergleicht.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Brauchen Sie etwas ganz besonders von hier?</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Immer in Freundschaft Ihr</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Der Druck der 9tn Ausgabe der "Select plants" beginnt jetzt. Vielleicht haben Sie noch einige Notizen zeitig für Aufnahme.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">28/3/95</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Would you be so kind, esteemed Professor, as to refer to this note?<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Apparent publication not identified.</p>
               </note> It cannot be about the <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Atriplex">Atriplex</name>
               </seg> species of Australia, certainly highly important for California, because the writer compares his plant with <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Medicago%20sativa">Medicago sativa</name>
               </seg>.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Do you need anything special from here?</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Always in friendship your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">The printing of the 9th edition of the <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Select plants</seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">B95.08.04</p>
               </note> is now beginning. Perhaps you have some more notes well timed for inclusion.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">There are some notes attributed to Hilgard in the ninth edition that were not in the earlier editions.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Atriplex">Atriplex</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Medicago%20sativa">Medicago sativa</name>
            </p>
